valueType.description:
The valueType of the field. Use with the corresponding {type of field}Value attribute. Signature and photo fields do not support values added via API. Their values must be omitted or set to null. For example:

```

"fields": [

  {

    "label": "Signature",

    "valueType": "ValueType_Signature"

  },

  ... more fields

]

```

VehicleStatsDecorations.description:
Optional decorations to the primary stat event. See [here](doc:decorations) for more details. The example shows the response if you were to submit `decorations=engineStates&obdEngineSeconds` to the query parameter:

```json
"decorations":{
  "engineStates": {
    "value": "Off"
  },
  "obdEngineSeconds": {
    "value": 9723103
  }
}
```
